metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
  VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
    FILTER(
      KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Tb_contratacoes'[Status])),
      NOT('Tb_contratacoes'[Status] IN {"Ativo"})
    )

  VAR __DS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      'Tb_contratacoes'[Status],
      __DS0FilterTable,
      "CountStatus", CALCULATE(COUNTA('Tb_contratacoes'[Status]))
    )

  VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
    TOPN(1002, __DS0Core, [CountStatus], 0, 'Tb_contratacoes'[Status], 1)

EVALUATE
  __DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
  [CountStatus] DESC, 'Tb_contratacoes'[Status]

metrics.visualTitle: Admissoes, Desligamentos e Saldo por Mês

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
  FILTER(
    KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Tb_contratacoes'[Status])),
    AND(
      'Tb_contratacoes'[Status] IN {"Saída voluntária"},
      NOT('Tb_contratacoes'[Status] IN {"Ativo"})
    )
  )

EVALUATE
  SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(__DS0FilterTable, "FuncionariosAtivos", IGNORE('Medidas'[FuncionariosAtivos]))

metrics.visualTitle: Admissoes, Desligamentos e Saldo por Mês

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
  VAR __DS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      'LocalDateTable_2efb5bfb-4a4e-454c-a67f-f3ef435efc57'[Mês],
      'LocalDateTable_2efb5bfb-4a4e-454c-a67f-f3ef435efc57'[MonthNo],
      "Admissoes", 'Medidas'[Admissoes],
      "Desligamentos", 'Medidas'[Desligamentos],
      "Saldo", 'Medidas'[Saldo]
    )

  VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
    TOPN(
      1001,
      __DS0Core,
      'LocalDateTable_2efb5bfb-4a4e-454c-a67f-f3ef435efc57'[MonthNo],
      1,
      'LocalDateTable_2efb5bfb-4a4e-454c-a67f-f3ef435efc57'[Mês],
      1
    )

EVALUATE
  __DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
  'LocalDateTable_2efb5bfb-4a4e-454c-a67f-f3ef435efc57'[MonthNo],
  'LocalDateTable_2efb5bfb-4a4e-454c-a67f-f3ef435efc57'[Mês]

DEFINE
  VAR __DS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      'LocalDateTable_2efb5bfb-4a4e-454c-a67f-f3ef435efc57'[Ano],
      "TurnoverGeral", 'Medidas'[TurnoverGeral],
      "TurnoverDesligamento", 'Medidas'[TurnoverDesligamento],
      "MinDate", IGNORE(CALCULATE(MIN('LocalDateTable_2efb5bfb-4a4e-454c-a67f-f3ef435efc57'[Date])))
    )

  VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

  VAR __DS0BodyBinnedSample = 
    SAMPLEAXISWITHLOCALMINMAX(
      3500,
      __DS0Core,
      [MinDate],
      [TurnoverGeral],
      [TurnoverDesligamento],
      350,
      ,
      ALPHABETICAL,
      ASC,
      105000,
      60
    )

EVALUATE
  ROW(
  "DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount
)

EVALUATE
  __DS0BodyBinnedSample

ORDER BY
  'LocalDateTable_2efb5bfb-4a4e-454c-a67f-f3ef435efc57'[Ano]

EVALUATE
  ROW(
  "FuncionariosAtivos", 'Medidas'[FuncionariosAtivos]
)

EVALUATE
  ROW(
  "Desligamentos", 'Medidas'[Desligamentos]
)

DEFINE
  VAR __DS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      'LocalDateTable_2efb5bfb-4a4e-454c-a67f-f3ef435efc57'[Ano],
      "TurnoverGeral", 'Medidas'[TurnoverGeral],
      "MetaTurnoverGeral", 'Medidas'[MetaTurnoverGeral]
    )

  VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
    TOPN(1002, __DS0Core, 'LocalDateTable_2efb5bfb-4a4e-454c-a67f-f3ef435efc57'[Ano], 0)

EVALUATE
  __DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
  'LocalDateTable_2efb5bfb-4a4e-454c-a67f-f3ef435efc57'[Ano]

DEFINE
  VAR __DS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      'LocalDateTable_2efb5bfb-4a4e-454c-a67f-f3ef435efc57'[Ano],
      "MetaAbsenteismo", 'Medidas'[MetaAbsenteismo],
      "Admissoes", 'Medidas'[Admissoes]
    )

  VAR __DS0BodyLimited =
